<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="row text-right" style="margin-top: 15px;">
      <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-2">
      <h2>My Clean Car</h2>
      <h4 style=" color: #00FF00;">book an eco wash</h4>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row" >
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h4>How it works?</h4>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-2">
        <%= image_tag "parking.png", style: "height: 45px; margin: 0px 5px;"%>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-10">
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">You have a vehicle, drive in town or in the countryside... you mess with it!<br>Every time your car is parked...it is an opportunity for us to take care of it!!!<br>My Clean Car is the opportunity for your car to be sparkling anywhere at anytime, thanks to a cleaner recommanded by other motorists</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-2">
        <%= image_tag "smartphone.png", style: "height: 45px; margin: 0px 5px;"%>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-10">
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">Connect to My Clean Car with your smartphone to order an outdoor cleaning of your car.<br>Fill in the application the mandatories informations about your car. Your car must respect cleaner security, easy access, and public reglementation.<br>A cleaner will accept your cleaning. As soon as you confirm this cleaning by paying, with our secured payment module. Your cleaning is booked.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-2">
        <%= image_tag "spray.png", style: "height: 45px; margin: 0px 5px;"%>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-10">
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">A cleaner will come to clean your car, at the desired time and at the location indicated. He will take care about your car respecting environnement and reglementation.
        We use only environmentally friendly products. No water or waste is issued on site</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-right"><%= link_to "back home", root_path %>
    </div>
</div>
